thread.title_full: Bake Me A Wish! reviewed by PATRICIA

author: PATRICIA
title: PATRICIA
text:
This is 3rd yr ordering sister's B-day cake sent 2-FL from PA. She said, "Very Good"! Perfect packaging, not a piece broken off. Tried gluton free cake an she said, " fabulous"! Everyone loved it! Will order for sons b-day in Feb., daughters in April! AWESOME! You need to share coupons for multipal cakes ordered in one year!
PA LEFEVER
Millersville, PA
